properties.title: He Was Just Dressed Like It, But He Didn't Smell Like it
properties.description: Non Paratus posted a photo: If he had been smoking what he's campaigning to legalize I think we would have all smelled it in the small courtyard in front of the main library. The guy showed up at Jerry Brown's get-out-the-vote rally to get publicity for Proposition 19, which would (supposedly) legalize small amounts of cannabis for recreational use. (Whether it remains a federally enforceable offense remains to be seen.) [Follow-up: Prop 19 did not pass. I'm sure this guy was disappointed.]
